432     // NOTE: A dummy context has to be created for opengl32.dll to load the
433     //       OpenGL ICD, from which we can then query WGL extensions
434     // NOTE: This code will accept the Microsoft GDI ICD; accelerated context
435     //       creation failure occurs during manual pixel format enumeration
